WEEK 04 PROGRESS REPORT

EdgeCloud Monitor – Sprint 2 Edge Telemetry Integration and Sprint 3 Alert Service Preparation

Overview

During Week 04, development focused on completing Sprint 2 Edge Telemetry integration activities for EdgeCloud Monitor.

The primary objective was to implement and validate the Edge Telemetry Agent and establish end-to-end communication between edge devices and the cloud-native monitoring platform. This included telemetry collection, telemetry transmission, heartbeat integration, database persistence validation, Docker Compose testing, API Gateway integration, and supporting technical documentation.

The week concluded with initial planning and preparation activities for Sprint 3 Alert Service development.

